02:39:14,510 --> 02:39:21,060
of electric force floating dangerous and deadly
across the frozen, ultra-cold plain.

2387
02:39:21,060 --> 02:39:23,590
And the expeditions brought back data.

2388
02:39:23,590 --> 02:39:31,050
Yet still Gresth Gkae could not sleep, his
thoughts intruding constantly.

2389
02:39:31,050 --> 02:39:34,260
Hours Merth Skahl spent with him, calming
him to sleep.

2390
02:39:34,260 --> 02:39:37,279
"But what is this constant search?

2391
02:39:37,279 --> 02:39:41,470
It is little enough I know of science, but
why do you send our men to these spots of

2392
02:39:41,470 --> 02:39:45,220
wonderfully beautiful, but useless natural
forces.

2393
02:39:45,220 --> 02:39:50,530
Can we somehow, do you think, turn them against
the people of these worlds?"

2394
02:39:50,530 --> 02:39:52,870
Softly the old Miran smiled.

2395
02:39:52,870 --> 02:39:55,600
"Yes, you might say so.

2396
02:39:55,600 --> 02:40:00,600
For look, it is the strange balls of electric
force I want to know about.

2397
02:40:00,600 --> 02:40:04,689
Sthor had few, but occasionally we saw them.

2398
02:40:04,689 --> 02:40:07,100
Never were they properly investigated.

2399
02:40:07,100 --> 02:40:12,930
I want to know their secret, for I am sure
they are balls of electric forces not vastly

2400
02:40:12,930 --> 02:40:16,850
dissimilar from the nucleus of the atom.

2401
02:40:16,850 --> 02:40:22,439
Always we have known that no system of purely
electrical forces could remain stable.

2402
02:40:22,439 --> 02:40:25,420
Yet these strange balls of energy do.

2403
02:40:25,420 --> 02:40:27,110
How is it?

2404
02:40:27,110 --> 02:40:30,380
I am sure it will be of vast importance.

2405
02:40:30,380 --> 02:40:35,930
But the direct secret I hope to learn is in
