2407
02:40:40,650 --> 02:40:45,810
If I can learn how to make these electric
balls of energy, can I not hope to make similar

2408
02:40:45,810 --> 02:40:47,250
magnetic balls of energy?"

2409
02:40:47,250 --> 02:40:52,240
"Yes, I see—that would seem true.

2410
02:40:52,240 --> 02:40:54,850
But what benefit would you derive from that?

2411
02:40:54,850 --> 02:40:59,270
You have magnetic beams now, and yet they
are useless because you can get nowhere near

2412
02:40:59,270 --> 02:41:00,359
the forts.

2413
02:41:00,359 --> 02:41:02,790
How then would these benefit you?"

2414
02:41:02,790 --> 02:41:07,979
"We can do nothing to those forts, because
of that magnetic shield.

2415
02:41:07,979 --> 02:41:13,600
Could we once break it down, then the fort
