infra-X-rays of theirs burn holes in our ships,

2418
02:41:21,010 --> 02:41:22,750
and—in our men.

2419
02:41:22,750 --> 02:41:29,080
"But look you, I can drop many atomic bombs
from a distance where their beams are ineffective.

2420
02:41:29,080 --> 02:41:34,160
Suppose I do make a magnetic ball of energy,
a magnetic bomb.

2421
02:41:34,160 --> 02:41:37,760
Then—I can drop it from a distance!

2422
02:41:37,760 --> 02:41:43,120
We have learned that the power supply of these
forts is very great—but not endless, as

2423
02:41:43,120 --> 02:41:47,940
