where they cannot reach us—and drop magnetic

2425
02:41:53,550 --> 02:41:54,550
bombs.

2426
02:41:54,550 --> 02:41:58,270
Ah, they will be stopped, and their energy
absorbed.

2427
02:41:58,270 --> 02:42:04,260
But we can keep it up, day after day, and
slowly drain out their power.

2428
02:42:04,260 --> 02:42:09,120
Then—then our atomic bombs can destroy those
forts, and we can move on!"

2429
02:42:09,120 --> 02:42:13,260
But suddenly the animation and strength left
his voice.

2430
02:42:13,260 --> 02:42:16,850
He turned a sad, downcast face to his friend.

2431
02:42:16,850 --> 02:42:21,779
"But Merth Skahl, we can't do it," he complained.

2432
02:42:21,779 --> 02:42:28,450
"Ah—now I can see why you so want to continue
this wearing and worrying work.

2433
02:42:28,450 --> 02:42:32,510
You need time, Gresth Gkae, only time for
success.

2434
02:42:32,510 --> 02:42:37,600
Tomorrow it may be that you will see the first
hint that will lead you to success."

2435
02:42:37,600 --> 02:42:44,260
"Ah—I only hope it, Merth Skahl, I only
hope it."

2436
02:42:44,260 --> 02:42:51,399
But it was the next day that they saw the
first glimpse of the secret, and saw the path

2437
02:42:51,399 --> 02:42:54,590
that might lead to hope and success.

2438
02:42:54,590 --> 02:42:57,800
In a week they were sending electric bombs
across the laboratory.

